    <text id="A0009T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>A. D. Dunlap tells his mother about the crops, his living expenses, and his daily
                    activities. Dunlap plans to build a house and mentions his intended.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1860-06-15">June 15 1860</date>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute><orig reg="Dear">Dire</orig> Mother</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>In <orig reg="haste">hast</orig> I take my pen in hand to write you a few lines
                    to let you all know that we <orig reg="are">ar</orig> well <orig reg="and"
                    >an</orig> hoping these few lines may find you all the same news of <orig
                        reg="interest">interrest</orig> is scarce <orig reg="her">here</orig> at
                    present. The weather is very hot at this time here we <orig reg="have">hav</orig>
                    <orig reg="been">ben</orig>
                    <orig reg="blessed">blesed</orig> with plenty of <orig reg="rain">rane</orig>
                    now for the last 8 weeks corn looks well <orig reg="and">an</orig>
                    <orig reg="some">som</orig>
                    <orig reg="again">a gane</orig> looks bad <orig reg="wheat">wheet</orig>
                    <orig reg="there">thare</orig> wont be any worth <unclear>nomin</unclear>
                    <orig reg="and">an</orig> oats is very short <orig reg="there">thare</orig> has
                        <orig reg="been">ben</orig>
                    <orig reg="several">sevrel</orig> storms here in the last 2 weeks <orig
                        reg="and">an</orig>
                    <orig reg="hail">hall</orig> plenty <orig reg="and">an</orig>
                    <orig reg="done">don</orig> a heap of <orig reg="damage">damige</orig>
                    <orig reg="there">thare</orig> was one man killed 15 miles from here another
                    town of Clinton <orig reg="by">bi</orig>
                    <orig reg="lightening">litngning</orig> his name was Ashby he was in a horse
                    stable at the time Mother times is hard here <orig reg="and">an</orig> I expect
                    will <pb n="2"/> be harder before they get <orig reg="better">beter</orig> the
                    fruit is scarce <orig reg="there">thare</orig> is plenty of <orig reg="peaches"
                        >peache</orig> in some <orig reg="places">plases</orig>
                    <orig reg="and">an</orig>
                    <orig reg="some">som</orig> few <orig reg="apples">apels</orig></p>

                <p>..well.. Mother I must tell you that I am <orig reg="going">gowing</orig> to
                    change my <orig reg="way">wa</orig> of living this <orig reg="fall">foul</orig>
                    if nothing <orig reg="happens">hapins</orig>
                    <orig reg="and">an</orig> I <orig reg="would">wold</orig> like to <orig
                        reg="hear">hare</orig> what you will say to it I <orig reg="have">hav</orig>
                    got tired living this <orig reg="way">wa</orig> for it costs <orig reg="too"
                    >to</orig> much to <orig reg="live">liv</orig>
                    <orig reg="alone">a lon</orig> in this country <orig reg="we">wee</orig>
                    <orig reg="are">ar</orig> paying two dollars <orig reg="and">an</orig> a half a
                        <orig reg="piece">pese</orig> a week <orig reg="and">an</orig> we <orig
                        reg="have">hav</orig> to furnish our <unclear>own</unclear> bed <orig
                        reg="and">an</orig> pay for our <orig reg="washing">washin</orig>
                    <orig reg="besides">be sids</orig> I <orig reg="have">hav</orig>
                    <orig reg="some">som</orig> notion to <orig reg="build">bild</orig> a house this
                    summer I <orig reg="aint">ant</orig>
                    <orig reg="certain">sertin</orig> whether I will or not we <orig reg="have">hav</orig>
                    <orig reg="about">a bout</orig> twelve hundred dollars
                    <unclear>standing</unclear> out here <orig reg="and">an</orig> still hoc as much
                    up we both can do I is working <orig reg="and">an</orig> on wagons <orig
                        reg="pretty">porty</orig> much all the time he is work at one now we earn
                        <orig reg="about">a bout</orig>
                    <pb n="3"/> one hundred <orig reg="and">an</orig> twenty dollars per month but
                    mother I've the <orig reg="everlasting">averlastin</orig> chills we <orig
                        reg="can't">cant</orig> get rid <orig reg="of">or</orig> them they <orig
                        reg="give">giv</orig> him <orig reg="and">an</orig> I thunder <orig
                        reg="sometimes">som times</orig> but <orig reg="don't">dont</orig> last long</p>

                <p>well Mother I <orig reg="traded">treded</orig>
                    <orig reg="horses">horsis</orig> this morning <orig reg="and">an</orig> got a
                    fine mare worth 200:00 I will cut a dash I <orig reg="reckon">recon</orig>
                    <orig reg="and">an</orig> there is <orig reg="two">to</orig> bed <orig
                        reg="dance">dans</orig> here <orig reg="tonight">to knigh</orig> I expect be
                    there with my <orig reg="intended">in Tended</orig> but I <orig reg="can't">cant</orig>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> you all know that the <orig reg="health">helth</orig> or the
                    country is very good at present except the chills <orig reg="and">an</orig> that
                    we <orig reg="don't">dont</orig> call sickness here <orig reg="Mother"
                    >Mothe</orig> I <orig reg="have">hav</orig>
                    <orig reg="some">som</orig> money <orig reg="and">an</orig> you <orig
                        reg="shall">shal</orig>
                    <orig reg="have">hav</orig> it well <orig reg="dear">Dire</orig>
                    <abbr expan="Mother">Mot</abbr> I will close for this time I <orig reg="have"
                        >hav</orig>
                    <pb n="4"/>
                    <orig reg="wrote">wrot</orig> all the news that I <orig reg="have">hav</orig>
                    <orig reg="and">an</orig>
                    <orig reg="have">hav</orig> not <orig reg="rote">wrote</orig> much <orig
                        reg="neither">nether</orig>
                    <orig reg="yes">yess</orig>
                    <orig reg="there">thare</orig> is to be several <orig reg="barbecues"
                    >barbacues</orig> round here <orig reg="the">th</orig> 4 of July <orig reg="and"
                        >an</orig> one on the 14 I wont know whether I shal be at any or not</p>

                <p>no more <orig reg="give">giv</orig> my best respects all <orig reg="and">an</orig>
                    <orig reg="especially">espocly</orig> uncle Jim I tell him I wont be <orig
                        reg="like">lik</orig> him <orig reg="lone">lon</orig>
                    <orig reg="and">an</orig> old <orig reg="bachelor">bachler</orig> all my life
                    tell sister Nan to look out <orig reg="and">an</orig> Mag the same</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>no more at present but remain <orig reg="your">youre</orig> most <orig
                            reg="dearest">direst</orig> son</salute>
                    <signed>A. D. Dunlop</signed>
                    <seg type="postscript">write soon to me and dont <orig reg="forget">for
                        get</orig> me</seg>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
